Privacy Policy

Effective Date:  08.08.2024

1. Introduction

Thank you for using our application "Lego Home Helper" ("App"). We understand that your privacy is important and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and how we protect your information.

2. Data Collection

Our app does not require registration and does not collect personal data from users. We do not store or transmit any data such as your name, email, or phone number.

3. Data Usage

Since the app does not collect your personal data, we do not use any data for analytics, marketing, or any other purposes. The app is solely used for inventorying your LEGO sets and does not have access to your device beyond this function.

4. Third-Party Services

Our app does not use third-party services that may collect information that identifies you. We do not integrate third-party analytics, advertising networks, or other external platforms.

5. Data Security

We take all necessary measures to ensure the security of data in our app. However, given the absence of data collection, the risks to your privacy are minimal.

6. Children's Policy

Our app is not intended for use by children under 13 years of age. We do not collect personal data about children and do not provide them access to content that may be inappropriate for their age.

7. Changes to Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. We recommend periodically reviewing the policy to stay informed of any updates.

8. Contact Information

If you have any questions or suggestions regarding our privacy policy, please contact us at yariyan@yandex.ru.
